text: Sabah Al Khalid Al Sabah (born 3 March 1953) is a Kuwaiti diplomat and politician who has been the Crown Prince of Kuwait since 2024. In November 2019, he became the Prime Minister of Kuwait. He was Prime Minister until 24 July 2022. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Kuwait Category:Princes and princesses
title: Sabah Al-Khalid Al-Sabah
